    <note>Ren(1) Ao [19187] Both Zhou Jiayou, 3.330-331 and XTS, 73A.19b trace the ancestor of the Lean Ren(1) to Ao, but there is a gap in both genealogies between Ao and the ancestors of Yaxiang [19190], zaixiang of Tang Gaozong, and no link between the descendants of Yaxiang and the Song Ren(1). However, Zhou(1) Bida [7197], in his funerary inscription for a descendant, Xu [19200], obviously has a detailed genealogy of the lineage not used by the compilers of either the NanBei shibiao or Tang zaixiang genealogical tables.</note>
